{"tid":1108264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［巴拿馬總統同我都算有啲交情] 17歲女坐郵輪被姦法官稱無「司法管轄權」釋放疑犯","createTime":"2019-04-15T23:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T23:55:13.000Z","uid":86199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b54de03e480d3443c8eb2af5407ca1a951e2e3","tid":1108264,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:52:50.000Z","msg":"英國一名17歲少女與父母乘搭郵輪「神曲號」（MSC Divina）到地中海度假，卻在郵輪上懷疑被一名男子強姦，郵輪船長待船隻抵達西班牙瓦倫西亞港口後報警，當地警方上船拉人。但當地法院同日稍後卻釋放疑犯，因為法官聲稱今次案件涉及兩名外國人士，而且案發地點是一艘正在國際水域航行、在巴拿馬註冊的郵輪，因此他「沒有司法管轄權調查這宗罪案」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190416&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59491128\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190416%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59491128&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCdwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=6084c1d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190416%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59491128&h=eebae72c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190416&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59491128</a>"},{"pid":"7c6580938b93626777c765ff752f1e3529314d69","tid":1108264,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:55:04.000Z","msg":"上船殺人"},{"pid":"f230150fcb11599fdb0a4409ae39de203bd92550","tid":1108264,"uid":86199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T23:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1YUKsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1YUKsZ.png&h=bb47d7af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SBxFE1j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSBxFE1j.png&h=b2d1f6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gZwMGk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gZwMGk.png&h=30196e2c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}